Dan Soder is a NYC-based comedian and actor who’s best known as ‘Mafee’ on Showtime’s Billions and for his time hosting SiriusXM’s The Bonfire with Big Jay Oakerson.

Dan’s most recent comedy special, Son of a Gary, is currently streaming on @HBO Max, along with The Standups on @Netflix and Not Special on @ComedyCentral. Other credits include: @ComedyCentral’s Half Hour, Conan, Inside Amy Schumer, and @midnight.
